.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-AUTOPILOT-STATUS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-autopilot-status \- show channel balance summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-autopilot-status
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns aggregate channel balance and capacity info.
Autopilot is not available in Core Lightning; this verb reports balance ratios
that help manual rebalancing decisions.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"active_channels":N, "total_capacity_msat":N, "local_balance_msat":N,
 "balance_ratio":N, "autopilot":"not_available"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-local-balance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-balance-ratio (1)
